*/5 0-1,5-23 2-31/3 * * create-dnsmasq-toggle-conf public vod
0   2        2-31/3 * * remove-dnsmasq-toggle-conf public vod

# YouTube
#   Available: at 02:00 - 05:00 on 3,6,9,12,15,18,21,24,27,30
*/5 *        1-31/3 * * create-dnsmasq-toggle-conf public youtube
*/5 *        2-31/3 * * create-dnsmasq-toggle-conf public youtube
*/5 0-1,5-23 3-31/3 * * create-dnsmasq-toggle-conf public youtube
0   2        3-31/3 * * remove-dnsmasq-toggle-conf public youtube
